# Vercel only needs the app source (Root Directory = app/apps/web) and
# installs its own deps + builds remotely, so exclude deps/build output and
# repo-root research/audit artifacts. Keeps the upload small (the full repo
# is ~1.2GB with node_modules). Do NOT exclude app assets (public/).
